sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_include_fa4f53f1074c5010d379ffa08c1ed012
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.AutoDLS</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>AutoDLS</name><script><![CDATA[var AutoDLS = Class.create();
AutoDLS.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {
    },
	
	loadImportSet: function(reqItemID, dataSourceID){
		
		var dataSource = new GlideRecord("sys_data_source");
		dataSource.get(dataSourceID);
			//gs.getProperty("global.auto.dls.data.source"));
gs.print("1-loading into de data source");
		GlideSysAttachment.copy('sc_req_item', reqItemID, 'sys_data_source', dataSource.sys_id);

		// Process file into data source record
		var loader = new GlideImportSetLoader();
		var importSetRec = loader.getImportSetGr(dataSource);

		// Import data from data source to import set table (based on form import type selection record)
		var ranload = loader.loadImportSetTable(importSetRec, dataSource);
		importSetRec.state = "loaded";
gs.print("2-Import set loaded");
		return importSetRec.update();
		
	},
	
	transform: function(set){
gs.print("3-Before transforming.." + set);

		var transformMapID = gs.GetProperty("global.auto.dls.transform.map");
		var transformWorker = new GlideImportSetTransformerWorker(set, transformMapID);
		transformWorker.setBackground(true);
		transformWorker.start();
gs.print("4-Transform");

		//Inform the user that a email outlining the status of the import will be sent once the import is complete
		gs.addInfoMessage("ImportSet Loaded");
	},

    type: 'AutoDLS'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2020-04-09 10:00:20</sys_created_on><sys_id>fa4f53f1074c5010d379ffa08c1ed012</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>AutoDLS</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_fa4f53f1074c5010d379ffa08c1ed012</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-04-09 15:08:37</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
